Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_1_The_Third_Plate,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_2_Thirteen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:08.52,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your battle \Nroyale victory, Hayama Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.35,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you are an official member of Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:12.99,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a shit about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.01,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, set up the \Nresearch lab for Jun and me—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.22,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.17,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, you have\N your first assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.66,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:27.17,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Once and for all, finish off the opponent\N you've already defeated twice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.37,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this, Hayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.01,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Central right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:35.34,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to join Central, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.74,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.62,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you listen to Azami-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.89,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,there's no guarantee that he'll \Nlet you do what you want—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:43.98,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.01,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way we \Ncan continue our research?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:48.48,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it, Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.69,Flashback Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.69,Flashback Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even get how much everything \Nwe've been through means to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.63,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:56.40,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:58.62,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.66,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what I have to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:06.58,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the chicken-fried bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.54,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:44.62,sign_6424_110_Food_Wars,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:44.62,sign_1937_22_The_Third_Plate,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)}The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:44.62,sign_1975_23_Totsuki_Train_Ar,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1150,1)}Totsuki Train Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:49.02,sign_3937_31_For_Whom,Sign 0246,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(501,477)}For Whom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.73,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The bear dish prepared by the master \Nof fragrance, Hayama Akira—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.44,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,chicken-fried bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, where's mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, and let me try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:00.91,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.13,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.74,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,After you've tasted it and\N accept defeat, leave the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.70,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're really acting like you \Nhave no time for me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.50,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I've always felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.42,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,We're no longer on equal footing.\N Get that through your thick skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.37,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,He's really confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.55,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,He must've had to walk the same tightrope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.36,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,of smelliness and umami, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.35,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.78,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,The first test is whether \Nhe succeeded in his wager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.93,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,to remove the smelliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.51,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,But there isn't much to doubt there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.27,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,On to the tasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.31,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The light batter is shining\N so brightly, it's almost blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.73,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama's skills are the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.11,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.99,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Just bringing it close to your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.58,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,is enough to make the spices sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.91,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if I may!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.17,Main Dialogue,BSh,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.45,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,No, Berta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.76,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.47,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Cilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.60,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stay calm and analyze this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.31,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,This pungent spiciness is the \Npiperine from black pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:18.26,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Its synergy with pyrazine, an aromatic \Ncompound resulting from heating paprika,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.32,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,has formed the foundation of \Nthe dish's flavor profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.53,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Thyme is countering bear meat's gaminess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.99,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Thymol, that sharp and\N astringent compound, is at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.20,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and cayenne and oregano's... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.91,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.88,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing all sense of reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.34,Italics Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,How exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:43.15,Italics Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,The bear meat's smelliness has been \Nconverted into a powerful umami in its entirety!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:48.62,Italics Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,The complex buildup of umami \Nand the layers of flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.91,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,This clearly surpasses\N Yukihira Soma's creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.02,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the obvious Cajun spice mix,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:01.18,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I've added to the marinade juniper berries\N that have been crushed with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.99,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,a mortar and pestle to\N heighten their fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.22,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,The more you chew,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.79,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,the more the exquisite and \Neven sweet umami of the bear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.87,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,should spread like a torrent \Nthrough your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.29,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-dono even chose \Nsmellier parts of the bear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.21,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,and used schisandra berries to \Nenhance the bear's flavors—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.88,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,And that wasn't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.55,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,It must mean that Hayama's spice use
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:23.01,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,skills are that much higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.98,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Even humans are said to be able to tell apart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.72,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,several thousand to nearly \Nten thousand odors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:33.18,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I simply used that ability in this dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.31,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.41,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,As if anyone could've made that dish
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.90,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,without Hayama's superhuman\N sensitivity and sense of smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.11,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.12,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I wouldn't have thought \Nto use a blow torch to sear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.16,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,the fish to bring out \Nthe oils and fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.29,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you come up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.73,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:02.28,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't take a back seat next \Ntime now that I know your tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.20,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.92,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys come here to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.89,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.67,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.64,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,But I have something I want to protect,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.85,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means defeating you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.45,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't surpass Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.91,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,That means that, with this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.83,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,...Yukihira-dono's expulsion is confirmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.57,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,It is too early to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:41.58,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,We have merely tasted the \Nfried meat by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.55,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,We have yet to taste it with the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.24,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.88,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to finish the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.85,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll dip Hayama-san's \Nfried bear into the gravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.78,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,A sauce made from deglazed\N bear fond, with a generous dose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.06,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,of the juniper berry's fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.82,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.15,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,An offshoot of the chest-baring \Nability that the Nakiri clan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.05,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,has passed down for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.93,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,The explosive tearing of \Ncloth due to willpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.87,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,also known as "The Explosion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.87,sign_10356_119_The_Explosion,Sign 0713,0000,0000,0000,,The Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.83,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.54,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,A flavor bombardment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.91,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,It is almost terrifying \Nhow polished this dish is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:27.21,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Juniper berries and Cajun spices!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.82,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Spiciness and sweetness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.85,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,A golden ratio to enhance \Nthe bear meat's flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.22,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,He has achieved the perfect balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.98,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,It is the result of his \Nscientific pursuit of how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.43,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,fragrance and deliciousness \Nare interconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.45,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to make an analogy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.73,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,it demonstrates ironclad \Nperfection from every angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.69,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,The dish is akin to an impenetrable fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.56,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can catch up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.66,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's just not possible without \Nmy superhuman sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.14,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.08,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "finished"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:03.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.54,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The final bell hasn't been rung yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:20.14,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll have Yukihira Soma's \Nminced meat cutlet with the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.60,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:26.94,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Like Hayama-san's sauce, this seems\N to be based on bear broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:27.48,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.69,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,The schisandra berries steeped \Nin sake provide a focal point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.15,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,What a gentle garlic fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.49,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this mildness coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.91,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.04,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,In comparison to Hayama's juniper berries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.25,Italics Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-chin used {\i0}that{\i1} ingredient \Nas the main player in the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.95,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.89,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.15,Italics Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,The entire dish has taken\N a 180 degree turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.19,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,What a lingering fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:56.05,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Thought persistent, it's not clinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:59.72,Italics Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though the bear meat's sweet \Nflavors have been sharpened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.03,Italics Dialogue,BSh,0000,0000,0000,,...and are rushing right through you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.08,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.98,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Our clothes came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.58,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.07,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,This technique is the more advanced \Nversion of the earlier Explosion ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.03,sign_13309_160_The_Explosion,Sign 0916,0000,0000,0000,,The Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.03,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,More advanced than The Explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:21.91,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Upon tasting a dish full of spiritual \Nharmony that is worthy of chest-baring,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:27.18,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,the willpower that flows in a Nakiri's \Nveins is unleashed as a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:35.34,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,This temporarily imparts the \Nbaring ability to outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.06,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,It is known as The Gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.22,sign_13831_166_The_Gift,Sign 0939,0000,0000,0000,,The Gift
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.00,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,The Gift?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.93,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-dono was able \Nto create such a dish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:47.52,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, this secret behind this \Nsauce's delicious flavors
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.99,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,are honey and balsamic vinegar, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.43,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The honey's faint sweetness brings \Ndepth of flavor to the sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:58.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and the vinegar's acidity brings the \Nflavors together into a sharp focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.99,Italics Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,No, depth and sharpness alone \Ncannot result in strong flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.45,Italics Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,This fragrance... is from caramelization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.42,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The honey has been slowly caramelized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.17,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That's an oxidation process that occurs \Nwhen you heat sugars, right, Berta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.33,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Cilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:18.43,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important technique that is \Nemployed in a wide range of dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.93,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,from French cuisine to sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,First, I slowly caramelized the honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,then thinned it with balsamic vinegar \Nuntil it reached a good consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I then added garlic and minced onions \Nthat had been sauteed separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.40,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and simmered it with schisandra berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:37.82,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I added the bear broth \Nand seasoned it with salt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:43.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,to create the ultimate sauce, which can \Naccelerate the minced bear cutlet's flavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.04,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.18,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.99,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,He enhanced bear meat with honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.79,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,then used balsamic vinegar \Nand caramelization to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.46,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,"subtract" and "emphasize."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.32,Flashback Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I managed to demonstrate \Ntwo theoretically opposing principles—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:02.39,Flashback Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,the subtraction of aroma and its emphasis— \Nin unison with this single dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:08.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I decided to use the principles \Nyou used in the finals against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.86,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,He really can't let go when \Nit comes to a match, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:17.07,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I do like that about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:22.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Akira's chicken-fried bear was \Nan exquisite and elegant dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The fried meat itself was \Noverwhelmingly superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:30.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,However, if we were to judge \Nthe sauce on its own merits,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:36.00,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma is the victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.21,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,He caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.97,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,But who's the overall victor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:41.59,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.80,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin evaluations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.51,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri Soue-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.72,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Cilla-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.93,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Berta-dono—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.64,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Please cast your votes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.94,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,If the fried meat and the sauce \Nare judged together as a whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:59.65,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,which dish achieved better success \Nin showcasing the bear's flavors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.32,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I've made my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.99,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.16,Main Dialogue,BSh,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:12.79,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,A split vote!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.74,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean they're equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:19.25,Main Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,For whom will you cast your \Nfinal vote, Nakiri Soue-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.21,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,An impeccable umami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.64,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,An impregnable fortress on one hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.97,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,and a siege machine that focuses all of \Nits flavors into one strike on the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.93,Italics Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Which one will Nakiri Soue-dono choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:37.15,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,My chicken-fried bear had no flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.11,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,But he's managed to catch up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.57,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.74,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.11,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.58,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:52.33,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,In this match, both of you \Nare near equals in flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:55.79,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,That is reflected by Berta \Nand Cilla's split vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.74,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a factor \Nthat'd decide the outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.51,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be one's obsession with one's dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:07.43,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma, you did not use just \Nany honey in the sauce, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:12.89,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, the faint tannic notes of \Nthis honey's fragrance are from—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I used honey from the Amur cork tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.59,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,A honey from a member of the Rutaceae family,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.94,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,the same family as the mandarin orange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.31,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's known for having a light sweetness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.28,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,and a faintly bitter aftertaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.26,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Other types of honey could \Nhave complemented the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.74,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,bear meat with richness and mellowness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:39.46,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,but it could have led to an \Noverly-heavy flavor profile
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.92,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,if its flavors simply amplified the \Nminced meat cutlet's strong punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.38,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,But when the honey from the \NAmur cork tree is used...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.85,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,The faint bitter and tannic aftertaste
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.27,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,is an excellent match with the bear meat—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.85,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,it is almost miraculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:56.39,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma did not overlook the \Npotential drawbacks of using honey
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.98,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,and pursued better taste\N to a far greater extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.38,Main Dialogue,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,But how'd he come up with this combination?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:06.40,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's hard to believe he was randomly \Ninspired to use this particular honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:11.15,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I was done in by you at \Nthe Moon Festival, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.90,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta admit, you never \Ngive up until you find an
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.95,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,answer you're satisfied with, Yukihira-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.69,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything you find that \Nmight work as an ingredient,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.08,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,please let me know right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.09,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's scrounge up as many ideas \Nas we can find before sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.59,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.34,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,We've found acorns and kiwi berries for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.72,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,We've gathered Yezo spruce leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.78,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:34.56,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:37.32,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go over to the ridge next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:37.89,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:38.86,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:41.09,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go down to the creek!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.61,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.89,Flashback Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go as long as we can
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.63,Flashback Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,to increase our options as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.86,Flashback Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll test everything out at the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:53.66,Flashback Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna test dozens and hundreds, \Neven thousands of combinations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.89,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll be going into the \Nmountains again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.96,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.25,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:03.01,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese RS members are well trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.90,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,You can abuse them as long \Nas you don't kill 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.26,Flashback Dialogue,Chinese RS,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.03,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So we just scrambled \Naround all over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and finally found honey as an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.22,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a lot of kinds of honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.31,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,so it took a little longer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,to settle on Amur cork tree honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.17,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,What lies at the very \Nfoundation of this dish
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.99,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,is none other than a chef's boundless \Ncuriosity and obsession with flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.45,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,There, I see who the chef is as an individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.37,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.12,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The deciding factor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:41.08,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,was to what degree the dish was \Na reflection of the chef as an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.14,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The one who deserves victory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.44,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,is the chef who best pursued his own cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:50.63,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The chef who truly sought \Nwhat his cooking should look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.72,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.97,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,How can he possibly reach my dish's \Nlevel of sophistication—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.94,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.30,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Dojima...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:01.94,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying you pursued true gourmet \Ndining to the best of your abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.80,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.42,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I constructed a sublime \Nand perfect balance of—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.89,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,All by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.24,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,without even knowing who you're cooking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.03,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.98,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Hayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.98,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It has such a rich smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.41,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.16,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the top student at Totsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.12,Flashback Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.58,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.31,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.74,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,But should I use a coarser grind of \Nthe spices used in the Cajun blend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.55,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,to let the flavors stand out more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.76,Flashback Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Jun—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.10,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even need to taste the dish to know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.44,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,that this dish is clearly \Ndifferent from what you served
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.65,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,at the Autumn Elections finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:55.25,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Akira, can you \Nsay with utter sincerity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.12,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,that you approached this \Ndish with true passion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.58,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,and did everything you could \Nduring the testing process?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:05.77,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,Were you perhaps missing the zealous desire to\Nhave someone say that the dish is delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:15.18,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Then how'd Yukihira...\NHow'd he get as far as he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:18.55,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd your motivation come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:22.32,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Were you really that greedy \Nabout your dish because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.31,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,you wanted to survive the advancement exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.44,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The hell you talking about, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was for you! All for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I was gonna make \Nyou eat the dish, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.82,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was all to make {\i1}you{\i0} say it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,To crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been working so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:43.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't stand to see you all distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.00,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here's one piping hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in, Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.98,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.11,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira's passion for this dish—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:22.08,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,all of his trials and tribulations—\Nare flooding into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.25,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,He kept me in squarely in his sights, \Neven though I'd closed myself off,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.71,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,and only thought about \Nhow to improve this dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.88,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't me, who'd lost \Nsight of why he was cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:37.89,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,and could only wear himself down to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:40.93,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.93,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:46.71,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.12,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:50.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here, Shiomi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.69,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.19,Main Dialogue,D,0000,0000,0000,,We know each other from our\N Polar Star Dormitory days, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.10,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,That was a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.44,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Jun's never hit me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.66,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also your guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.16,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,so think of that as parenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:08.30,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to tell you my conclusions \Nafter thinking about all that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.98,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a research lab anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.65,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted you to do more
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.58,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,than I wanted to get my \Nequipment and budget back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:20.59,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.87,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What I've really wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:29.67,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,is you really enjoying your cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:34.77,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and devoting yourself to your craft \Nwith lots of friends your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.42,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a kid, Hayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.57,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to feel responsible \Nfor the research group shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.93,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't treat me like a kid, Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.63,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.88,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, I don't care what Central does,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I still want to work on cooking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you give up on your own cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.06,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.15,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.69,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.44,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually really enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.59,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you let me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.85,Italics Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's like... a message from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.42,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.29,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.92,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.76,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,With a vote of two to one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.55,Main Dialogue,Soe,0000,0000,0000,,we declare Yukihira Soma the victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:27.29,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to call home now, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:28.93,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.45,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just come to Polar Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You'll at least have somewhere to cook, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:40.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiomi-senpai, you used to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We have tons of empty rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:42.85,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:43.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Say "yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:45.13,Main Dialogue,J,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:47.27,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:49.84,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:52.64,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:54.55,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nakiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:56.55,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:00.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I managed to redeem myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.47,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:05.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.44,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.87,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:16.33,sign_33396_399_Aide_to_Nakiri_A,Sign 2314,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)}Aide to Nakiri Azami \N Aida Sean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.33,Main Dialogue Top,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,I am Aida, Azami-sama's aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.22,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:22.45,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Akira, you understand \Nwhat is happening, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:22.79,Main Dialogue,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:27.38,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Given the most recent results, \Nyou are being expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:32.77,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,We have received reports from exams that \Nhave occurred on other routes, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:36.93,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama... I am so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:43.56,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.39,Main Dialogue,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,All of the above have been expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.92,sign_30623_420_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_410_Next_Episode__De,Sign 2407,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode  {\fs16}Declaration of War
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_412_Food_Wars,,0000,0000,0000,,Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.92,sign_34668_413_The_Third_Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:10.03,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's go to the station up north!
